  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Private Family Chauffeur",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>Provide safe and reliable transportation for the Director and guests, run errands, and maintain the cleanliness and condition of the owner’s Toyota Alphard vehicle while adhering to traffic laws and ensuring confidentiality. The company has a work pass quota, but is subject to the issuance of a work permit by the Ministry of Manpower.  </p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive the Director and guests safely to destinations within Singapore, assisting passengers with entering and exiting the vehicle and handling luggage or items</li><li>Transport passengers to school or tuition locations as required</li><li>Run errands and deliver documents, packages, or items efficiently across Singapore</li><li>Maintain the cleanliness and proper upkeep of the Toyota Alphard vehicle</li><li>Follow all traffic laws and regulations to ensure safe driving with a clean driving record</li><li>Use maps and GPS systems effectively to navigate local roads and routes</li><li>Communicate clearly and professionally with the employer and others as needed</li><li>Maintain strict confidentiality regarding the employer’s personal and professional matters at all times</li><li>Adapt to flexible work schedules and perform additional duties as assigned</li><li>Standby and provide driving support during weekends, Public Holidays, and extended hours when required</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Class 3/3A driver’s license</li><li>Clean driving record</li><li>Sound knowledge of road safety regulations</li><li>Working knowledge of local roads and routes</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Non-smoker preferred</li><li>The company has a work pass quota, but is subject to the issuance of a work permit by the Ministry of Manpower.  </li></ul><ul><li>Working Location: Bukit Timah</li><li>Working Days 5.5 days (Weekdays work starts at 6:45am for school days)</li></ul><p>Please send your CV to 85220391 </p>",
